title.narrative: Partnership for Transforming Health Systems 2 - Procurement of Goods

description.narrative: This activity (Partnership for Transforming Health Systems 2 - Procurement of Goods) is a component of Partnership for Transforming Health Systems 2 reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of goods' and a budget of £40,915,603. This component benefits Nigeria, and works in the following sector(s): Basic health care, Infectious disease control, Reproductive health care. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-10-2008 and the end date is 31-10-2016.
